# Problem

**Generative AI is becoming a core part of browser search experience**

Brave *wants* to build their own AI search assistant – Leo

Deliver more value to ~~users~~ than their competitors

> Quotes look like this — a paragraph with the vertical line on the left.

```js
// code blocks live at the top level, with optional syntax highlighting
const chatbot = await brave.leo.ask('What do users actually need?');
```

# Defining research questions with stakeholders

{% table %}
- Hi
- Hello
---
