## Categorizing our insights

Participants positive experiences show what already works well today and pain-points show where we can improve as compared to other chatbots.

## What worked well

Users find follow-up prompt suggestions helpful in directing their conversation with a chatbot, especially during web searches.

> **Users find summaries of articles generated by chatbots to be helpful when browsing the web.**
